transcripts.text: One of the things God put on my heart when I travel around the world is to bring greetings from our brothers and sisters from one part of the world to the other brothers and sisters elsewhere around the world.  Okay, one, two, three.  One, two, three.  One, two, three.  Shalom!  Come, you who are here!  Shalom!  Shalom!  Shalom from Berlin, South Africa!  Shalom from East Slovenia!
